attributes.title: GTA V - Escape Escort
attributes.description: GTA with facecams! Ryan, Michael, and Gavin force Jeremy to record this special episode from his now twelve-foot-tall desk. Hopefully Jeremy's new found height will be an advantage as the crew heists their way through more Import/Export DLC.

attributes.title: GTA V - Breakdown Recovery and Cleanup Op
attributes.description: Ryan, Michael, Gavin and Lil J continue to plow through the Special Vehicle Works missions, this time with the cantankerous Wastelander and the amphibious Blazer Aqua.Music Credit: "Blue Danube" from Audio Network

attributes.title: GTA V - Asset Seizure and Firewall Protection
attributes.description: Jack fills in for Lil J as the Fake AH Crew continue their run of Special Vehicle Works missions, this time with the Jobuild Phantom Wedge and the Coil Rocket Voltic.

attributes.title: GTA v - Cunning Stunts 5
attributes.description: Geoff really enjoyed the Ramps! Ramps! Ramps! map he played with Game Attack, so Achievement Hunter goes back to attempt more Cunning Stunts. Glorious.

attributes.title: GTA V - Jack Bag 2
attributes.description: Jack's back with his super sack! They'll hit the track and try not to get whacked in this episode that is jam packed.

attributes.title: GTA V - Coast Guard Duty
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter finally completes all of the Import/Export DLC Special Vehicle Works missions, with a heist featuring the Imponte Ruiner 2000 for the grand finale. Also, Ryan tries to murder Gavin with a helicopter.

attributes.title: GTA V - Verified Cunning Stunts
attributes.description: Geoff, Ryan, Matt, Jeremy, Michael, and Gavin return to the cunty-stunty world of Cunning Stunts! The Achievement Hunter boys have raised their standards, so they're not settling for any ol' shit maps this week. No! They're ready to tear into some Rockstar Verified Cunning Stunt Contest winning maps!

attributes.title: GTA V - Offense Defense: Back to Basics (#7)
attributes.description: Geoff makes the boys plays his favorite game mode in GTA, and Ryan obsesses over another man's member. Welcome back to Offense Defense!

attributes.title: GTA V - Deadline 2: Thin Dead Line
attributes.description: The Achievement Hunter boys are Tronning it up in GTA V Deadline. But it's not Tron. Legally, at least.

attributes.title: GTA V - Mario Bag
attributes.description: When you don't have blue shells and bananas, rockets and sticky bombs will have to do! Geoff's Mario themed playlist features GTA races and a Last Team Standing gamemode, all modded by the GTA community.

attributes.title: GTA V - Achievement Knievel 2017
attributes.description: Everyone's wanted another Achievement Knievel with the new CEO vehicles, and today we deliver! The creator mode in GTA doesn't let us use the new cars, though, so rather than a Things to Do In, we're releasing a full Let's Play as we build the longest Knievel stunt jump in Let's Play GTA history.

attributes.title: GTA V - Cunning Stunts 6
attributes.description: It's the ultimate showdown: Betting Buddies vs. Battle Buddies vs. Bike Buddies vs. Lindsay. May the fastest, cunning-est, stunty-est team win!

attributes.title: Let's Play - GTA V - The Fleeca Job - Criminal Masterminds (Part 1)
attributes.description: The Fake AH Crew have learned that you can earn $10,000,000 for completing the Criminal Masterminds challenge in GTA. All they have to do is beat every heist mission on hard, with the same four players, without dying once. Piece of cake, right?

attributes.title: GTA V - Special Cunning Stunts
attributes.description: Rocket cars in Cunning Stunts! Knight Rider cars in Cunning Stunts! It's finally happened; we're finally doing it. Lannan "Lazarbeam" Eacott is along for the joyride.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Prison Break: Setup - Criminal Masterminds (Part 2)
attributes.description: They survived the Fleeca Job, so it's time for Achievement Hunter to strap on some helmets and gear up for the next round of Criminal Masterminds. Ryan, Michael, Jeremy, and Gavin must steal a plane, a police bus, a muscle car, and a police bus schedule as they prepare to break Maxim Rashkovsky out of prison.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Prison Break - Criminal Masterminds (Part 3)
attributes.description: Time for Heist no. 2 in the Criminal Masterminds series! Ryan, Gavin, Michael, and Jeremy must break into Bolingbroke Penitentiary to free Maxim Rashkovsky. It's going to be quite the show, so sit down, pop some P's & Q's in your gob, and enjoy the ride!

attributes.title: GTA V - Special Cunning Stunts 2
attributes.description: The Fake AH Crew rocket down to the race track, get blazed, and ruin their reputations as they do their second Special Cunning Stunts episode.

attributes.title: Hot Seat: GTA V Featuring James Buckley
attributes.description: Hotseat returns with a special guest, YouTuber and British Actor James Buckley. Geoff and Gavin interviewed the Inbetweeners star at the Funhaus studio, with Bruce and Lawrence joining in on the fun.

attributes.title: GTA V - Humane Raid: Setup - Criminal Masterminds (Part 4)
attributes.description: The tension continues as the Fake AH crew start the Humane Raid Heist in their quest for the Criminal Masterminds achievement. Will they complete the setup? Will they bum cheese it all up? The only way to know is to watch! Or, you know, read the comments. But don't do that. That would ruin the fun.

attributes.title: GTA V - Humane Raid: Setup - Criminal Masterminds (Part 5)
attributes.description: Three setups down, two setups to go! The Criminal Masterminds at Achievement Hunter are so close to doing the Humane Labs Raid Heist, but first they must steal a Valkyrie helicopter and plant an EMP-laden truck at the Humane Labs. Can these weasely sneaks catch the guards with their pants down, or are they about to get seriously stomped?

attributes.title: GTA V - The Humane Labs Raid - Criminal Masterminds (Part 6)
attributes.description: It's time, ladies and gentlemen, for a Heist! You've watched them cake walk through the Fleeca Job. You saw them scramble through the Prison Break. Can these incompetent fools possibly succeed at the Humane Labs Raid? There's only way way to find out without being a cheaty-cheat and looking up spoilers in the comments, so sit back, enlarge the video, and see what's in store for the wannabe Criminal Masterminds at Achievement Hunter.

attributes.title: GTA V - Tiny Racers
attributes.description: Geoff, Jack, Jeremy, and Michael try out the newest and cutest racing mode in GTA Online!

attributes.title: GTA V - Series A: Setup - Criminal Masterminds (Part 7)
attributes.description: The AH boys use a helicopter to board a party yacht, kill some frat brothers, and steal their cocaine. Will they soar through this Criminal Masterminds challenge... or will they crash and burn?

attributes.title: GTA V - Series A: Setup - Criminal Masterminds (Part 8)
attributes.description: Tensions have never been higher between our criminal masterminds as Ryan, Gavin, Michael, and Jeremy take on the legendarily difficult Trash Truck mission.

attributes.title: GTA V - Series A: Heist - Criminal Masterminds (Part 9)
attributes.description: Yee-haw, boys! We got ourselves one of them G-T-A criminal masterminds heists. Them there O'Neil fellers got themselves a meth lab, and I reckon them redneck basterds gon' wanna keep that meth all to their lonesome. But Cletus and his honkies got nothin' on our B-A badass muthers, you know what I'm sayin'? Whaddaya say we start this hootenannie and end this Series A Heist for good? Git 'r done, boys!

attributes.title: GTA V - Rocket Bikes
attributes.description: Rocket Bikes! Burning up our 'chutes when they explode.The Fake AH Crew check out some new toys in their first foray into the Gunrunning DLC.

attributes.title: GTA V Jackbag: AH Live Stream
attributes.description: Thanks to Dollar Shave Club for supporting our Live Stream. Jack, Michael, Ryan, Geoff, and Matt as they take on The AH Audience in some GTAV races.

attributes.title: GTA V - Pacific Standard: Setup - Criminal Masterminds (Part 10)
attributes.description: The greatest minds in Achievement Hunter spring into action as they set up the final heist in the Criminal Masterminds series.

attributes.title: GTA V - Pacific Standard: Setup - Criminal Masterminds (Part 11)
attributes.description: Ryan, Jeremy, Gavin, and Michael need to rob the military and some bikers to prepare for the final heist in the Criminal Masterminds series.

attributes.title: GTA V -  Pacific Standard: Heist - Criminal Masterminds (Finale)
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter takes on the Pacific Standard Heist in the finale to the Criminal Masterminds series.

attributes.title: GTA V - Severe Weather Patterns (Mobile Operations #1)
attributes.description: The boys help Ryan beat the new Mobile Operations mission with the Dune FAV military buggy.

attributes.title: GTA V - Exit Strategy (Mobile Operations #2)
attributes.description: Jack, Jeremy, Michael and Ryan return to finish the Gunrunning Missions: Half-track Bully, Exit Strategy, and Offshore Assets.

attributes.title: GTA V - Cover Blown (Mobile Operations #3)
attributes.description: The boys shoot some missiles, run some guns, bike some rockets, and complete their missions in the finale to the Mobile Operations series in GTA Online.

attributes.title: GTA V - Risky Rocket Runway
attributes.description: The boys go to the airport to screw around with their rocket bikes. Gavin: When both wheels touch a surface, you recharge your boost. And the back of a titan is a surface. So why don't we try that shite?

attributes.title: GTA V - Chopper vs. Chopper
attributes.description: Five rocket-powered bikes against one rocket-shooting helicopter. 'Nuff said.

attributes.title: GTA V - Overtime Shootout
attributes.description: It's Monkey Ball! No, wait, it's GTA V. Sorta hard to tell the difference with the new Overtime Shootout game mode.

attributes.title: GTA V - Special Cunning Stunts 3
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter races in another GTA V Special Cunning Stunts full of hazardous jumps, wicked tricks, epic fails, and glorious wins.

attributes.title: GTA V - Overtime Shootout: Early Rumblings (#2)
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter completes the Overtime Shootout maps before mercilessly shoving each other off the scoring platforms in Overtime Rumble.

attributes.title: GTA V - Geoff Bag
attributes.description: It's Geoff Bag, a mushy mix of Geoff-curated GTAV games! Cars face off against RPGs for some funny moments as we play Last Team Standing.

attributes.title: GTA V - Smuggler's Run
attributes.description: Bombers and gliders and planes, oh my! Achievement Hunter tries out the new vehicles from the Smuggler's Run DLC update to GTA Online.

attributes.title: GTA V - Cunning Stunts feat. Robbie Kay
attributes.description: British actor Robbie Kay joins Achievement Hunter for a special playlist of Cunning Stunts races.

attributes.title: GTA V - Geoff Bag 2
attributes.description: Geoff Bag returns, featuring a giant billiards derby, motorcycle racing insanity, and Last Team Standing on a floating Yoshi platform.

attributes.title: GTA V - Motor Wars
attributes.description: In GTA Online's PUBG-inspired battle royale mode, Achievement Hunter face off using old and new vehicles of mass destruction.

attributes.title: GTA V - Transform Races
attributes.description: In Transform Races, players mix race types as they switch between land, sea, and air tracks, using Supers and Off-Roads, Boats, Planes, and Helicopters.

attributes.title: GTA V - Slasher 3: Spooky Edition
attributes.description: The slasher game mode in GTA Online returns for spooky scary Halloween.

attributes.title: GTA V - Transform Races: Transformers 2: The Sequel (#2)
attributes.description: We mix race types and switch between land, sea, and air tracks, using Supers and Off-Roads, Boats, Planes, and Helicopters. Also rocket cars.

attributes.title: GTA V - Offense Defense: Sauce Party (#8)
attributes.description: Alfredo is introduced to the smash-tacular Offense Defense gamemode in GTA Online.

attributes.title: GTA V - Transform Races: Transformers in Time (#3)
attributes.description: Watch our supercars transform as they switch from races by land, sea, and sky! GTA Online's metamorphosis-based stunt race returns.

attributes.title: GTA V - Bat Car
attributes.description: Everyone buys the Grotti Vigilante, a weaponised vehicle from the Smuggler's Run update. It's totally not the Batmobile.

attributes.title: GTA V - Transform Races: Rage of Extinction (#4)
attributes.description: Transform Races are the evolution of racing in GTA Online. Watch us jump ramps, cruise, skydive, and barrel roll to the finish line!

attributes.title: GTA V - Geoff Bag 4
attributes.description: Time for more Geoff Bag, featuring some Snipers vs. Stunters, infernal Mario Kart, and the most difficult stunt race ever. Geoff!

attributes.title: GTA V - The Data Breaches: Prep - Doomsday Heist (#1)
attributes.description: Achievement Hunter steal an ambulance, some Deluxos, and an Akula in Act 1 of the Doomsday Heist DLC.

attributes.title: GTA V - Setup: The Data Breaches - Doomsday Heist (#2)
attributes.description: To setup the Data Breaches Heist, we steal an Akula and use the Deluxos to hack multiple target vehicles - including a rather large cargo plane.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Data Breaches: Heist - Doomsday Heist (#3)
attributes.description: We use the Akula to infiltrate the server farm at the N.O.O.S.E. Government Facility, then begin the first heist in the Doomsday Heist DLC.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Bogdan Problem: Prep - Doomsday Heist (#4)
attributes.description: We steal some keycards, take out Agent ULP's kidnappers, tart a riot, steal the Riot Control Van, and boost some wrecked Strombergs.

attributes.title: GTA V - Slashers Adversary Mode
attributes.description: We went to New York to visit Rockstar HQ and test out their new Slashers Adversary game mode.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Bogdan Problem: Setup - Doomsday Heist (#5)
attributes.description: We steal the Avenger from Merryweather, rescue Agent ULP at the foundry, and use water cannons on the RCV to secure stolen hard drives.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Bogdan Problem: Heist - Doomsday Heist (#6)
attributes.description: We use the Strombergs to scan a submarine, board it through an airlock, and disable it, while holding off enemy agents in the Avenger above.

attributes.title: GTA V - The Doomsday Scenario: Prep - Doomsday Heist (#7)
attributes.description: We steal a duffel bag full of money, eliminate an arms dealer, and acquire a Chernobog ballistic missile launcher.
